&lt;ul class="org-ul"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.linuxcapable.com/how-to-redirect-non-www-www-with-nginx/"&gt;How to Redirect NON-WWW &amp; WWW with Nginx - LinuxCapable&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
