&lt;li&gt;元搜索（多个独立搜索引擎的集合，&lt;a href="https://github.com/tianheg/whoogle-search"&gt;https://github.com/tianheg/whoogle-search&lt;/a&gt;，&lt;a href="https://searxng.github.io/searxng/"&gt;https://searxng.github.io/searxng/&lt;/a&gt;，&lt;a href="https://www.excite.com/"&gt;https://www.excite.com/&lt;/a&gt;）&lt;/li&gt;
